company_name: PLANTA TABAK-MANUFAKTUR DR. MANFRED OBERMANN GMBH & CO. KG
information: The company PLANTA TABAK-MANUFAKTUR DR. MANFRED OBERMANN GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1953, which operates in the Tobacco and smokers items industry. It also operates in the Tobacco industries. It is based in Berlin, Germany.
